Model definition for Taskqueue.TaskqueueStats. Statistics for the TaskQueue object in question. This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Taskqueue service. To reduce the data transferred during service requests, you may remove members that contain data elements that your application does not need. For a detailed explanation, see: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/Json
